CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780589464
OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FExperts say vapes laced with spice are
OL,8,Fbeing sold to children via social
OL,9,Fmedia platforms and are 'blatantly and
OL,10,Fpervasively available', as Amelia
OL,11,FBeckett reports.
OL,13,FWarning: There are details in this
OL,14,Freport that some might find distressing
OL,16,FVape liquids laced with drugs that put
OL,17,Fone 12-year-old boy in a coma are
OL,18,Fbeing sold over social media sites.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780589464
OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FDespite this, Good Morning Britain has
OL,8,Ffound that when the accounts are
OL,9,Fflagged and removed from those sites,
OL,10,Fnew ones almost immediately pop back
OL,11,Fup.
OL,13,FFreddie Fenson was 11 years old when
OL,14,Fhe started vaping.
OL,16,FBy the age of 12, he says he was
OL,17,Finfluenced by friends to start trying
OL,18,Fwhat he thought was a THC vape - the
OL,19,Factive ingredient in cannabis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780589464
OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FWithin a week, he said he was hooked
OL,8,Fand began smoking them every day.
OL,9,FHowever, instead of THC, it was in
OL,10,Ffact the highly addictive and
OL,11,Fdangerous synthetic drug, spice.
OL,13,FTwo months later, he collapsed, was
OL,14,Frushed to the hospital and placed in
OL,15,Fan induced coma for two weeks.
OL,17,F"That drug, that took over my life. It
OL,18,Ftook away my money, took over my
OL,19,Fhealth," Freddie said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780589464
OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,F"Literally not even like two months of
OL,8,Fsmoking every day, I landed in a coma,
OL,9,Fand my lung collapsed."
OL,11,F"I spent two months in hospital, and I
OL,12,Fhad to learn to walk again, to talk
OL,13,Fagain, eat again, literally restart my
OL,14,Flife as a kid."
OL,16,FSpice was initially designed to mimic
OL,17,Fcannabis, but it's much stronger,
OL,18,Fhighly unpredictable, and
OL,19,Fsignificantly more dangerous.
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780589464
OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FBecause its chemical makeup constantly
OL,8,Fchanges, the effects vary widely and
OL,9,Fcan quickly become life-threatening.
OL,11,FDrug dealers often swap out THC for
OL,12,Fspice without telling the buyer
OL,13,Fbecause it is much cheaper and far
OL,14,Fmore addictive.
OL,16,F"Spice for me made me do whatever I
OL,17,Fcould to get it," Freddie said. "It
OL,18,Fsounds crazy, but I even stole money
OL,19,Ffrom my dad to get it.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780589464
OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,F"I may have only done that once, but
OL,8,Fthat time I stole was the lowest point
OL,9,FI ever went."
OL,11,FFreddie said he first came across the
OL,12,Fdrug being sold via Snapchat.
OL,14,F"It's everywhere. I wouldn't say it's
OL,15,Fan epidemic, but I think it could soon
OL,16,Fbe."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@MO]vD@AOUxD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780589464
OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FProfessor Chris Pudney at the
OL,8,FUniversity of Bath has been
OL,9,Finvestigating the prevalence of these
OL,10,Fvapes in schools and, in 2025, found
OL,11,Fthat as many as one in four
OL,12,Fconfiscated vapes contain spice.
OL,14,FHe has since been researching how
OL,15,Favailable it is on social media and
OL,16,Fhas found a network of ten thousand
OL,17,Faccounts linked to the sale of the
OL,18,Fdrug.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780589464
OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FProfessor Pudney said: "It's
OL,8,Fincredibly, blatantly and pervasively
OL,9,Favailable on these platforms. It's
OL,10,Fabsolutely overt drug dealing with the
OL,11,Fsocial media platforms being used as a
OL,12,Fshop windows to find as many customers
OL,13,Fas they possibly can."
OL,15,FHe flagged 74 of these accounts based
OL,16,Fin the UK to TikTok, but only half
OL,17,Fwere taken down. It wasn't until his
OL,18,Flocal MP wrote to them that the other
OL,19,Fhalf were removed.
OL,26,@oD@XOUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780589464
OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FHowever, since then, Good Morning
OL,8,FBritain has found a number of new
OL,9,Faccounts pop up under different names
OL,10,Fclaiming to sell "THC vape liquid",
OL,11,Fwhich Professor Pudney says is in fact
OL,12,Falmost certainly spice.
OL,14,F"A THC vape would cost around #60 to
OL,15,F#80, but these are being sold for as
OL,16,Flittle as #2. That is a major red
OL,17,Fflag", he said.
OL,19,FUnder the Online Safety Act, Ofcom now
OL,20,Fregulates TikTok and other social
OL,21,Fmedia platforms.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780589464
OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FBut Professor Pudney feels they aren't
OL,8,Fdoing enough to tackle this problem.
OL,10,F"Ofcom told us that drug dealing is
OL,11,Fnot one of their priority areas. We're
OL,12,Fhopeful with our continued work that
OL,13,Fcan change, but at this point, they
OL,14,Fare not going to be taking any
OL,15,Fenforcement action against these
OL,16,Fplatforms," he said.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780589464
OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,F"The problem is so blatant and
OL,8,Fobvious, the evidence is so easy to
OL,9,Faccumulate that we can't understand
OL,10,Fwhy the regulator wouldn't at least
OL,11,Fask the platforms to sort it out
OL,12,Fbefore even doing formal enforcement."
OL,14,FFreddie said his concern is that until
OL,15,Fsomething is done, so many other
OL,16,Fchildren could end up like him.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780589464
OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,F"I feel like the thing for me is the
OL,8,Fkids that are randomly scrolling, and
OL,9,Fthey end up coming across something
OL,10,Flike this, and they think 'what is
OL,11,Fthis, I'll buy it and try it,'"
OL,12,FFreddie said.
OL,14,F"That's what is scary because then
OL,15,Fthey could end up hooked like I was,
OL,16,Fso I really want to speak out to try
OL,17,Fand stop it from happening to other
OL,18,Fpeople."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
