OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FA spokesperson for Ofcom said: "The
OL,8,Fsale or promotion of drugs to children
OL,9,Fis illegal, and platforms like TikTok
OL,10,Fand Snap must ensure children are
OL,11,Fprotected from it on their platforms.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@oD@`OU
