SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780589464
OL,3,CVapes laced with 'spice' that put boy,
OL,4,C12, in coma sold to kids on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,F"Wherever this falls short, we will
OL,8,Ftake action. Insights from academics
OL,9,Flike Professor Pudney are crucial to
OL,10,Four work in enforcing the Online
OL,11,FSafety Act, and we remain open to
OL,12,Freceiving further evidence on this
OL,13,Fmatter."
OL,15,FTikTok said: "The trade of illegal
OL,16,Fproducts is not permitted on TikTok.
OL,17,FWe remove 99% of the violating content
OL,18,Fwe find before it's reported, and
OL,19,Fshare helpful resources when people
OL,20,Fsearch for terms related to smoking or
OL,21,Fvaping."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@HO]
