OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FSnapchat said: "Snapchat prohibits
OL,8,Fillegal activities, such as unofficial
OL,9,For unlawful vape sales. We proactively
OL,10,Fdetect and remove content relating to
OL,11,Fillicit drugs and vapes, we employ
OL,12,Ftechnology to block related search
OL,13,Fresults; and we provide easy-to-use in-
OL,14,Fapp reporting tools. We also retain
OL,15,Fcontent that is removed for an
OL,16,Fextended period in case of valid
OL,17,Fpolice requests.
OL,26,@oD@POU
