OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,F"Recognising that no single company
OL,8,Fcan eliminate every online threat, we
OL,9,Fconsistently adapt our strategies,
OL,10,Fwork with trusted third parties, and
OL,11,Fcollaborate across industry and
OL,12,Fsociety to help keep Snapchatters
OL,13,Fsafe."
